== Installation == 

Install the CPAN Options module:

 [phil@optimus Workspace]$ cpan Options


Unpack the dist archive:

 [phil@optimus Workspace]$ tar zxvf dist-1.1.tar.gz


Make a symlink in /usr/local/bin for dist:

 [phil@optimus Workspace]$ cd dist
 [phil@optimus      dist]$ sudo ln -s dist.pl /usr/local/bin/dist

